  <div id="home">
    <section id="hero" class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20" style="padding-top: 150px; padding-bottom: 150px;">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-white text-[2rem] sm:text-4xl md:text-7xl lg:text-9xl leading-snug sm:leading-tight mb-12" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-weight: 900; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
          <span class="font-extrabold whitespace-nowrap">Your Digital Marketing</span>
          <span class="text-[#CDFF00] underline decoration-[#CDFF00] decoration-4 underline-offset-8">Growth Partner</span>
          Here To Help You
          <span class="text-[#CDFF00] underline decoration-[#CDFF00] decoration-4 underline-offset-8">Dominate</span>.
        </h1>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl" style="font-family: Kanit, sans-serif;">
          <p><span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">Let's cut to the chase</span> — every time someone searches for...</p>
          <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-gray-700 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-mono text-white md:inline-block block" style="min-height: 4rem;">
            Best <span class="bg-[#2a2a2a] px-2 py-1 rounded inline-block" style="min-width: 14ch;"><span id="typewriter-word"></span><span id="typewriter-cursor">|</span></span> near me
          </div>
          <p>and clicks on your competition, <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">they're taking money straight out of your pocket.</span></p>
          <p>Meanwhile, it feels like you're <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">stuck juggling knives...</span> &quot;Post on Instagram! Start a podcast! Run some ads! Get a new logo!&quot;</p>
          <p>But here's the cold, hard truth: <em class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">If you're not killing it with your digital marketing strategy, you're bleeding opportunities.</em> Your competitors are eating your lunch, taking your calls, and stealing your customers.</p>
          <p>If you want to win — like, really win — <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">you need to own digital marketing, ensuring your brand stands out from the competition.</span></p>
          <p>And that's where we come in. KillerGrowth doesn't play nice. <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">We're here to help you dominate and grow.</span></p>
          <p>With a team of dedicated experts, razor-sharp strategies, and AI-powered precision, we'll slice through the noise and <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">keep the calls coming in.</span></p>
          <p>So, whether you're just getting started or ready to go for the jugular, <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">it's time to step up.</span></p>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-2xl"><span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">Let's sharpen the knives and kill it.</span></p>
          <a href="/booking" class="inline-block mt-8 bg-[#CDFF00] text-[#0D0D0D] px-8 py-4 text-xl font-bold rounded hover:bg-[#b8e600] transition-colors duration-300" style="font-family: Kanit, sans-serif;">Ready to <span class="font-black">KILL IT?</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
