  <div id="difference" class="scroll-mt-20 md:scroll-mt-24">
    <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#CDFF00] text-sm tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">THE KILLER DIFFERENCE</span>
          <h2 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mt-4" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;">Not Your Usual <span style="color:#CEFF00">Marketing Team</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="text-center"><div class="w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#CDFF00] to-transparent mb-8"></div><h3 class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;">We've Lived It</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" style="font-family: Kanit, sans-serif;">We're not just consultants — we're entrepreneurs who have started, scaled, and sold businesses. <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">We understand your challenges because we've been in your shoes.</span></p></div>
          <div class="text-center"><div class="w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#CDFF00] to-transparent mb-8"></div><h3 class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;">Results-Driven, Always</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" style="font-family: Kanit, sans-serif;">Every strategy we craft and every decision we make is rooted in driving measurable growth. <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">No fluff, no guesswork — just results.</span></p></div>
          <div class="text-center"><div class="w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#CDFF00] to-transparent mb-8"></div><h3 class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: Teko, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;">Partners, Not Providers</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" style="font-family: Kanit, sans-serif;">We don't work for you; we work with you. Our mission is to <span class="text-[#CDFF00] font-semibold">invest in your success and help you achieve your goals every step of the way.</span></p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
